modName: Ashara Princes of the Woods White and Brown Retexture
summary: A Retexture for the great Ashara Princess of the Wood Mod by SydneyB (Original Mod is Required)
descriptionHtml:
[color=#ff7700][size=3][b]ABOUT[/b][/size][/color]


This is my fourth Retexture, i wanted a whiter & brighter version of the Princess of the Wood by SydneyB

[size=3]http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/18008[/size]


YOU NEED the above mod in order to use this retexture.


There are two versions, one which is Bright White and the second which is a Light Brown.



I SUCK at taking nice Screens.. i do not have that much patience... so if anyone wants to upload some nice Screens with poses and stuff, be my guest.



[color=#ff7700][size=3][b]REQUIREMENTS[/b][/size][/color]


YOU NEED the following mod in order to use this retexture.

[size=3]http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/18008[/size]



[color=#ff7700][size=3][b]INSTALL[/b][/size][/color]


Decompress the files and just drag n drop into main Data folder:

C:/Program Files/Steam/Steamapps/Common/Skyrim/Data
